| Module                          | Signal      | TM4C123 Pin    | Port   |
| ------------------------------- | ----------- | -------------- | ------ |
| **Motor Driver (L293D)**        | IN1         | PA2            | Port A |
|                                 | IN2         | PA3            | Port A |
|                                 | IN3         | PA4            | Port A |
|                                 | IN4         | PA5            | Port A |
|                                 | EN1         | PB0 (PWM)      | Port B |
|                                 | EN2         | PB1 (PWM)      | Port B |
| **Bluetooth (HC-05)**           | TX          | PA1 (UART0 RX) | Port A |
|                                 | RX          | PA0 (UART0 TX) | Port A |
| **Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)** | TRIG        | PD0            | Port D |
|                                 | ECHO        | PD1            | Port D |
| **IR Sensor – Left**            | OUT         | PE1            | Port E |
| **IR Sensor – Right**           | OUT         | PE2            | Port E |
| **Mode Switch**                 | Manual/Auto | PF4 (SW1)      | Port F |
| **Status LED**                  | LED         | PF1 (Red)      | Port F |
